snippet.title: Mega Drive Longplay [495] Aerobiz Supersonic
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: JagOfTroy

Sequel to the first Aerobiz, this one gives a lot more options in each region to create flights. 

Again, all the scenarios are virtually the same other than different plane choices so I opted for the most current one this time. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
